Package: CARTEx
Title: CAR-T based exhaustion score
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Hima", "Anbunathan", email = "hima.anbunathan@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8458-4845"))
Description: Quantifies exhaustion profile for CD8+ T cells. The package also
    provides a pca based method to compute phenotype specific score for each
    gene, and scores single-cell objects (Seurat, AnnData/.h5ad, .h5Seurat,
    .loom) memory-efficiently with a transparent report of the assumptions
    behind each per-cell score.
